text: Jahangir Alam (born 6 June 1991) is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He made his List A debut for Uttara Sporting Club in the 2018–19 Dhaka Premier Division Cricket League on 23 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Uttara Sporting Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
